<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.1">
<l>taḻaikaḷun toṅkalun tatumpi yeṅkun</l>
<l rend="indent">taṇṇumai yekkamat taḷitāḻ pīli</l>
<l>kuḻalkaḷuṅ kītamu māki yeṅkuṅ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvintaṉ varukiṉṟa kūṭṭaṅ kaṇṭu</l>
<l>maḻaikolō varukiṉṟa teṉṟu colli</l>
<l rend="indent">maṅkaimār cālaka vācal paṟṟi</l>
<l>nuḻaivaṉar niṟpaṉa rāki yeṅku</l>
<l rend="indent">muḷḷamviṭ ṭūṇmaṟan toḻin taṉarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Seeing the friends that come [along with] Govinda</l>
<l rend="indent">waving peacock fans and peacock feathers,</l>
<l>with big drums, single-headed drums, flutes</l>
<l rend="indent">with dangling peacock feathers, and songs everywhere,</l>
<l>Maidens, grasping the opening of [their] latticed windows,</l>
<l rend="indent">exclaim,“That’s not the rain cloud coming is it?”</l>
<l>[and] while they creep [through their windows] and stand [in awe],</l>
<l rend="indent">they place [him] in the entirety of [their] hearts, </l>
<l>and forget to eat!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
